Gambian-born Nigerian actress, Rosaline Meurer, has stated that her husband, Olakunle Churchill, should be every man’s role model. The actress disclosed this on Friday via her official Instagram page after their family vacation overseas, expressing that her husband proved to her that soul mate truly exists. She wrote, “I love and admire you not because you’re my husband but because you are what every man should aspire to be. -Advertisement- “Until I met you I thought soul mate was just a myth. Thank you for being you, for sharing your love with me.. for helping me see the unique beauty in imperfection… for showing me that love is something you do; something not just to be said, but also to be shown. I LOVE YOU BABE @olakunlechurchill.”